    li.active: a(href=basePath+'/admin/messages/') 所有消息
    li: a(href=basePath+'/admin/messages/recv/') 收到的消息
    li: a(href=basePath+'/admin/messages/sent/') 发送的消息
    li.pull-right: a(href=basePath+'/admin/messages/new/')
      i.icon-plus 
      |  发送消息
  include message-browse

